      <div class="hero-kicker">Reef design system · v1.3.2</div>
      <h1>Design<br>in <em>Voi's</em><br>language.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Tokens, rules, and 35 components — every pattern your product team needs. The complete language for Voi's digital products.</p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="/foundation/colours" class="btn btn-contrast btn-lg">Explore tokens</a>
        <a href="/components/buttons" class="btn btn-outlined btn-lg">View components</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-photo-wrap">
