    <div class="feat">
      <div class="feat-copy">
        <div class="s-overline">Components</div>
        <h2 class="feat-heading">35 components.<br>Production-ready.</h2>
        <p class="feat-body">Every component is interactive, token-driven, and dark-mode aware. What you see here is exactly what ships — no extra translation needed.</p>
        <a href="/components/buttons" class="feat-link">Browse all components →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-visual">
        <div class="feat-frame">

          <div>
            <div class="feat-tag">Buttons · 6 variants</div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:10px">
